title: How to Find Your Passion
itunes:title: How to Find Your Passion
description:
Episode 167 - The question that I am most asked by my listeners is "How do I find my passion?" To be honest, I don't know if there is a correct way to answer that question. The only thing that I do know is that there are ways to open your mind up and to find a new passion, or remember what your childhood passion is. In this episode I dive into that topic.
